trans-unit.source: Exception occurs if passed to module learner has invalid type.
trans-unit.target: Exception occurs if passed to module learner has invalid type.

trans-unit.source: This exception occurs if a trained model is incompatible with the given score module.
trans-unit.target: This exception occurs if a trained model is incompatible with the given score module.

trans-unit.source: For example, connecting the output of <link xlink:href="fa4aa69d-2f1c-4ba4-ad5f-90ea3a515b4c" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">Train Matchbox Recommender</link> to <link xlink:href="401b4f92-e724-4d5a-be81-d5b0ff9bdb33" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">Score</link> instead of <link xlink:href="55544522-9a10-44bd-884f-9a91a9cec2cd" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">Score Matchbox Recommender</link> will cause this error.
trans-unit.target: For example, connecting the output of <link xlink:href="fa4aa69d-2f1c-4ba4-ad5f-90ea3a515b4c" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">Train Matchbox Recommender</link> to <link xlink:href="401b4f92-e724-4d5a-be81-d5b0ff9bdb33" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">Score</link> instead of <link xlink:href="55544522-9a10-44bd-884f-9a91a9cec2cd" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">Score Matchbox Recommender</link> will cause this error.

trans-unit.source: If the model was produced using the generic <link xlink:href="5cc7053e-aa30-450d-96c0-dae4be720977" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">Train Model</link> module, connect it to the generic <link xlink:href="401b4f92-e724-4d5a-be81-d5b0ff9bdb33" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">Score Model</link> module.
trans-unit.target: If the model was produced using the generic <link xlink:href="5cc7053e-aa30-450d-96c0-dae4be720977" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">Train Model</link> module, connect it to the generic <link xlink:href="401b4f92-e724-4d5a-be81-d5b0ff9bdb33" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">Score Model</link> module.

trans-unit.source: If the model was trained using any of the specialized modules (for example, <link xlink:href="8383eb49-c0a3-45db-95c8-eb56a1fef5bf" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">Train Vowpal Wabbit</link>), connect the trained model to the corresponding specialized score module.
trans-unit.target: If the model was trained using any of the specialized modules (for example, <link xlink:href="8383eb49-c0a3-45db-95c8-eb56a1fef5bf" xmlns:xlink="http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink">Train Vowpal Wabbit</link>), connect the trained model to the corresponding specialized score module.

trans-unit.source: Learner of invalid type is passed.
